Description: small OpenGL demo by The Bad Sectors, released in 2020
 Short real-time demo by Blueghost of The Bad Sectors, created for the Just For
 Fun 30 Seconds Demo Compo. Rendered using OpenGL 2.0.
 .
 The demo runs on systems with 64MB memory and supports fallback rendering
 on very old GPUs via texture combiners.

